Avocado Tomato Toast

10 min
$2.5
300 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 1

Allergens:

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free Option

Cuisine:

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

Description

A fresh, vibrant toast topped with creamy avocado and juicy tomatoes, perfect for a quick and satisfying meal.

Ingredients

  • bread: 2 slices
  • avocado: 1 ripe
  • tomato: 1 medium
  • lemon juice: 1 tablespoon
  • chili flakes: to taste
